@param.name: @param
@param.body:
height {Integer ? 16}
The height of the image. The default is 16.
@param.description: The height of the image. The default is 16.

@param.name: @param
@param.body:
width {Integer ? 16}
The width of the image. The default is 16.
@param.description: The width of the image. The default is 16.

@param.name: @param
@param.body:
cellInfo {Map} Information about the cell being renderered, including:
  • state
  • rowDiv
  • stylesheet
  • element
  • dataIndex
  • cellData
  • height
@param.description:
Information about the cell being renderered, including:
  • state
  • rowDiv
  • stylesheet
  • element
  • dataIndex
  • cellData
  • height

@return.name: @return
@return.body:
{Map} The returned map should contain at least the url field, but may contain any others of these:
url
The URL of the image to be displayed
imageWidth
The width at which the image should be displayed
imageHeight
The height at which the image should be displayed
extras
Any extra attributes to be include in the 'image' tag.
